title: Portfolio Redesign
start: 2026-02-02
schedule: business-days
owner: @me
version: 1.0

// Solo dev portfolio site redesign.
// Goal: ship a new portfolio by end of February.
// Mix of design, dev, and content work — mostly sequential with
// a couple of parallel phases where design and content can overlap.

# Research & Planning

[x] Audit current site              | 2h  | @me | %100 | id:audit
[x] Collect inspiration references  | 3h  | @me | %100 | id:inspo | after:audit
[x] List all case studies to write  | 1h  | @me | %100 | id:case-study-list
[x] Choose tech stack               | 2h  | @me | %100 | id:stack-chosen
// Went with Astro + Tailwind. Rejected Next.js (too heavy) and plain HTML (too slow to update).

# Design

[x] Sketch layout concepts         | 1d  | @me | %100 | id:sketches | after:inspo
[x] Choose color palette & type    | 2h  | @me | %100 | id:visual-system | after:sketches
[~] High-fidelity mockups          | 2d  | @me | %65  | id:mockups | after:visual-system
.  [x] Homepage mockup             | 3h  | @me | %100
.  [x] Case study page             | 3h  | @me | %100
.  [~] About & contact page        | 2h  | @me | %40
.  [ ] 404 and empty states        | 1h  | @me
[ ] Mobile layout review           | 1h  | @me | id:mobile-review | after:mockups
>> Design approved                  | id:design-done | after:mobile-review

# Content (parallel with late design)

parallel: content | after:case-study-list
[~] Case study: E-commerce rebuild  | 1d  | @me | %80 | id:cs-ecomm
[~] Case study: SaaS dashboard      | 1d  | @me | %50 | id:cs-saas | after:cs-ecomm
[ ] Case study: Mobile app          | 1d  | @me | id:cs-mobile | after:cs-saas
[ ] About page copy                 | 2h  | @me | id:about-copy
[ ] Homepage headline & sub-copy    | 1h  | @me | id:home-copy | after:about-copy
end: content

# Development

parallel: dev-setup | after:design-done
[ ] Scaffold Astro project          | 2h  | @me | id:scaffold
[ ] Configure Tailwind & fonts      | 1h  | @me | after:scaffold | id:tailwind-done
[ ] Set up component library        | 3h  | @me | after:tailwind-done | id:components-done
[ ] Deploy pipeline (Vercel)        | 1h  | @me | id:deploy-pipeline
end: dev-setup

parallel: dev-pages | after:dev-setup,content
[ ] Build homepage                  | 3h  | @me | id:homepage-built | after:components-done,home-copy
[ ] Build case study template       | 4h  | @me | id:cs-template | after:components-done
[ ] Populate case studies           | 2h  | @me | after:cs-template,cs-mobile | id:cs-done
[ ] Build about & contact pages     | 2h  | @me | after:components-done,about-copy
end: dev-pages

[ ] Dark mode implementation        | 2h  | @me | after:dev-pages | id:dark-mode
[ ] Animations & scroll effects     | 3h  | @me | after:dark-mode
[ ] Cross-browser testing           | 2h  | @me | after:dev-pages | id:xbrowser

# Polish & Launch

[ ] Lighthouse audit & fixes        | 3h  | @me | after:dev-pages | id:lighthouse
.  [ ] Performance (target 95+)     | 1h  | @me | id:perf-fix
.  [ ] Accessibility (target 95+)   | 1h  | @me | id:a11y-fix
.  [ ] SEO meta tags                | 1h  | @me | id:seo-fix
[ ] Write README for site repo      | 1h  | @me | after:lighthouse
[ ] Final review pass               | 2h  | @me | after:lighthouse,xbrowser | id:final-review

>> Ship to production               | id:launched | after:final-review | +deadline | <2026-02-28

# Nice to Haves

[>] Blog section                    | 2d  | @me
// Deferred: no content ready, don't want to ship empty
[>] Project filter / search         | 1d  | @me
// Deferred: only 6 projects, not worth it yet
